name: Idris_Solid_Sheesham_Wood_Console_Table_Dark_Sheesham
reviews: I was a little nervous to order something like this online without having seen it first, but I'm so very happy with this purchase! (I'm particular about wood furniture because my father was a woodworker. And it was hard to find something with these dimensions that wasn't veneer, which was why I ordered online.) The table has a beautiful wood grain and a lovely warm stain, and it's solidly built. I like how the drawer is not obvious but easy to open. It was very easy to screw the legs on. A perfect fit for our living room.
description: This remarkable Idris Solid sheesham wood console table has a rustic charm. The handcrafted table is made from 'green' materials. The irregular grain patterns, with its unusual knots and mineral deposits, give this table an appealing, natural look. The small, functional drawer is a great storage place for keys and other knick-knacks. A wonderful tie in for you living room or bedroom. StyleContemporaryMaterialWoodTypeConsole TablesFinishWood FinishAssemblyAssembly RequiredColorBrownProduct FeaturesEco-Friendly
